MoveCost Enum

Definition

Describes the move cost of a replica.

In this Article

public enum MoveCost
Inheritance
Enum
MoveCost

Remarks

When a new replica or service instance is created it will get a default value for move cost. This value will be selected based on the service: For replicas or instances of default services default move cost value will be , meaning that moving these replicas is free.For replicas or instances of other services default move cost will be .

Fields

High

Specifies the move cost of a replica as High.
Low

Specifies the move cost of a replica as Low.
Medium

Specifies the move cost of a replica as Medium.
Zero

Specifies the move cost of a replica as Zero.
